===灭绝的分类单元===

The name of an extinct taxon can be preceded by one of the following markers: <code>† &amp;dagger; <nowiki>{{extinct}}</nowiki></code>. Any of them will appear as † in the output. The † will not be italicized and will not be included in a wikilink.

